{"name":"Revenant serum","type":"cypher","img":"systems/cyphersystem/icons/items/cypher.svg","system":{"version":2,"description":"<p><strong>Level:</strong> 1d6 + 4</p><p><strong>Form:</strong> Injection or potion</p><p><strong>Effect:</strong> Brings a dead person back to life for a limited time as an obsessed creature called a revenant. The cypher can be used up to an hour before or after death (in anticipation of dying or in response to someone’s death) and requires up to an hour to take effect, at which time the creature recovers [[/r 1d6+6]] points to its Pools. The new revenant is usually obsessed with revenge on its killer or accomplishing one last task before truly dying again. A revenant has all the abilities it had when it was alive, but all its actions are hindered. It has the same appearance as before, except the wounds that killed it are still visible, and in general it has an unnatural look. It does not need to eat, drink, or sleep, but it can still rest if it wants to (such as to make a recovery roll). The revenant remains in this active state for one hour per cypher level, after which it dies again and cannot be reanimated with this cypher.</p>","archived":false,"basic":{"level":"1d6+4","identified":true},"settings":{"general":{"nameUnidentified":""}}},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"cyphersystem","systemVersion":"2.5.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1683654718519,"modifiedTime":1683655050999,"lastModifiedBy":"yThCrv1jSfPXOC2U"},"_id":"gzzJlqAN8mgrMFk5","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"yThCrv1jSfPXOC2U":3}}
{"name":"Insanity suppressor","type":"cypher","img":"systems/cyphersystem/icons/items/cypher.svg","system":{"version":2,"description":"<p><strong>Level:</strong> 1d6</p><p><strong>Form:</strong> Device, injection, or pill</p><p><strong>Effect:</strong> Temporarily negates insanity or a mental disorder in a creature (two such effects if the cypher level is 6 or higher). Example disorders include delusions, manias, compulsions, phobias, psychopathy, and schizophrenia. The creature loses all negative symptoms of their insanity or mental disorder for one day. Each day after that, the creature must make a level 1 Intellect defense roll to prolong the effect; failure means relapse. The roll is hindered by one step for each day that has passed since the cypher was used.</p>","archived":false,"basic":{"level":"1d6","identified":true},"settings":{"general":{"nameUnidentified":""}}},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"cyphersystem","systemVersion":"2.5.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1683654257162,"modifiedTime":1683655559105,"lastModifiedBy":"yThCrv1jSfPXOC2U"},"_id":"jaFwZlPOzU2WjIO8","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"yThCrv1jSfPXOC2U":3}}
{"name":"Anathema siren (extradimensional creatures)","type":"cypher","img":"systems/cyphersystem/icons/items/cypher.svg","system":{"version":2,"description":"<p><strong>Level:</strong> 1d6 + 2</p><p><strong>Form:</strong> Amulet or device</p><p><strong>Effect:</strong> Creates a strange and annoying noise about the volume of a human shouting. The noise is especially aggravating toward one type of creature; creatures of this type have all their actions hindered by two steps (hindered by three steps if the cypher level is 7 or higher) while within short range of the cypher. The user must use their action each round to manipulate the cypher for the noise and its effects to persist, or it goes silent and loses all power. The siren can be used for up to one minute per cypher level.</p>","archived":false,"basic":{"level":"1d6+2","identified":true},"settings":{"general":{"nameUnidentified":""}}},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"yThCrv1jSfPXOC2U":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.q348kJWAJe7sVS01"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"cyphersystem","systemVersion":"2.5.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1683650532312,"modifiedTime":1683656135567,"lastModifiedBy":"yThCrv1jSfPXOC2U"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"kwoblz3SJgPUBmXv"}
{"name":"Ghost detector","type":"cypher","img":"systems/cyphersystem/icons/items/cypher.svg","system":{"version":2,"description":"<p><strong>Level:</strong> 1d6 + 1</p><p><strong>Form:</strong> Amulet, crystal, or device</p><p><strong>Effect:</strong> Automatically indicates if a ghost, spirit, or similar entity is within a short distance (a long distance if the cypher is level 6 or higher). If the user takes an action to study or focus their attention on the cypher, they can narrow down what quarter-arc of a circle the ghost is in. If the ghost is normally invisible, it becomes somewhat visible (hindering its stealth attempts by one step). The cypher remains active for ten minutes per cypher level.</p>","archived":false,"basic":{"level":"1d6+1","identified":true},"settings":{"general":{"nameUnidentified":""}}},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"cyphersystem","systemVersion":"2.5.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1683651287149,"modifiedTime":1683655050997,"lastModifiedBy":"yThCrv1jSfPXOC2U"},"_id":"m1T7xBh4fvJFnxUk","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"yThCrv1jSfPXOC2U":3}}
{"name":"Homunculus flask","type":"cypher","img":"systems/cyphersystem/icons/items/cypher.svg","system":{"version":2,"description":"<p><strong>Level:</strong> 1d6 + 1</p><p><strong>Form:</strong> Ornate, opaque alchemical bottle filled with strange fluid</p><p><strong>Effect:</strong> To activate this cypher, you must open the bottle, add a few fresh drops of your blood (inflicting 1 point of Might damage to you), stopper it again, and leave it alone for one day. When the bottle is next unstoppered, a hand-sized creature called a homunculus crawls out; it vaguely resembles you and serves you for one day per cypher level before dissolving into useless goo. Each time you give it an order, you must make an Intellect defense roll against it; if you fail, it becomes free to ignore your commands (but might pretend to be obedient so it can plot against you). </p><blockquote><p>@UUID[Compendium.cyphersystem-compendium.basic-creatures-and-npcs.JjwGZc4XtYtmSmzt]{Homunculus}: level 2; alchemy, all defenses, and stealth as level 3</p></blockquote>","archived":false,"basic":{"level":"1d6+1","identified":true},"settings":{"general":{"nameUnidentified":""}}},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"cyphersystem","systemVersion":"2.5.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1683651465735,"modifiedTime":1683655050998,"lastModifiedBy":"yThCrv1jSfPXOC2U"},"_id":"n3lGX0s2rEAJmzDR","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"yThCrv1jSfPXOC2U":3}}
{"name":"Ascendant flesh vivisector","type":"cypher","img":"systems/cyphersystem/icons/items/cypher.svg","system":{"version":2,"description":"<p><strong>Level:</strong> 1d6 + 4</p><p><strong>Form:</strong> Device, injection, or pill</p><p><strong>Effect:</strong> If used on a beast of no larger than human size whose level is less than the cypher level, this radically alters the beast’s shape so it resembles a human being. The beast-human still thinks and acts like a beast, but it looks like a human and can perform actions using its human dexterity (such as turning a doorknob or walking upright). This transformation lasts for one day per cypher level, but after an equal amount of time the beast reverts to its normal shape (in the manner described for the ascendant brain vivisector cypher). Additional uses of the cypher tend to have diminishing returns. </p><blockquote><p>Using this cypher on a beast whose level is too high might end up temporarily transforming it into a human with bestial features.</p></blockquote>","archived":false,"basic":{"level":"1d6+4","identified":true},"settings":{"general":{"nameUnidentified":""}}},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"cyphersystem","systemVersion":"2.5.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1683650996993,"modifiedTime":1683655050996,"lastModifiedBy":"yThCrv1jSfPXOC2U"},"_id":"ohfJFNFl46EuNd7i","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"yThCrv1jSfPXOC2U":3}}
{"name":"Mind swapper","type":"cypher","img":"systems/cyphersystem/icons/items/cypher.svg","system":{"version":2,"description":"<p><strong>Level:</strong> 1d6 + 2</p><p><strong>Form:</strong> Amulet or device</p><p><strong>Effect:</strong> The user attempts to swap minds with a creature within short range that is no larger than a human. The target can make an Intellect defense roll to resist. If the swap is successful, the user gains control of the creature’s body (and vice versa). Physical abilities remain with the body, but mental abilities go with the mind; for example, an Adept with Onslaught (a mental ability) could take over the body of a Warrior with Swipe (a physical ability), and could use either of these while controlling the Warrior’s body. All actions of both creatures are hindered while the swap is in effect, although long-term practice in a mind-swapped body eventually overcomes this penalty. The swap lasts for one hour per cypher level, after which the two minds return to their previous bodies</p><blockquote><p>Clever users of a mind swapper have an ally restrain or sedate them before swapping minds so their target doesn’t cause trouble in the user’s body.</p></blockquote>","archived":false,"basic":{"level":"1d6+2","identified":true},"settings":{"general":{"nameUnidentified":""}}},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"cyphersystem","systemVersion":"2.5.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1683654481759,"modifiedTime":1683655050999,"lastModifiedBy":"yThCrv1jSfPXOC2U"},"_id":"ovaXKbgWjfNaP71X","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"yThCrv1jSfPXOC2U":3}}
{"name":"Anathema siren (werewolves)","type":"cypher","img":"systems/cyphersystem/icons/items/cypher.svg","system":{"version":2,"description":"<p><strong>Level:</strong> 1d6 + 2</p><p><strong>Form:</strong> Amulet or device</p><p><strong>Effect:</strong> Creates a strange and annoying noise about the volume of a human shouting. The noise is especially aggravating toward one type of creature; creatures of this type have all their actions hindered by two steps (hindered by three steps if the cypher level is 7 or higher) while within short range of the cypher. The user must use their action each round to manipulate the cypher for the noise and its effects to persist, or it goes silent and loses all power. The siren can be used for up to one minute per cypher level. Roll a [[/r d100]] to determine what sort of creature is affected:</p><table><tbody><tr><td>01–10</td><td>Aliens (probably one specific kind of alien)</td></tr><tr><td>11–16</td><td>Animate dolls and puppets</td></tr><tr><td>17–22</td><td>Cryptids</td></tr><tr><td>23–32</td><td>Demons</td></tr><tr><td>33–28</td><td>Doppelgangers</td></tr><tr><td>39–48</td><td>Ghosts</td></tr><tr><td>49–54</td><td>Mummies</td></tr><tr><td>55–64</td><td>Robots</td></tr><tr><td>65–70</td><td>Simulacra</td></tr><tr><td>71–80</td><td>Vampires</td></tr><tr><td>81–90</td><td>Werewolves (or some other werecreature)</td></tr><tr><td>91–95</td><td>Extradimensional creatures</td></tr><tr><td>96–00</td><td>Undead</td></tr></tbody></table>","archived":false,"basic":{"level":"1d6+2","identified":true},"settings":{"general":{"nameUnidentified":""}}},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"yThCrv1jSfPXOC2U":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.D4Jhe8m4GL4DZWMT"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"cyphersystem","systemVersion":"2.5.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1683650532312,"modifiedTime":1683656149025,"lastModifiedBy":"yThCrv1jSfPXOC2U"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"qqBrauJkPHI5qG0S"}
{"name":"Invisibility revealer","type":"cypher","img":"systems/cyphersystem/icons/items/cypher.svg","system":{"version":2,"description":"<p><strong>Level:</strong> 1d6 + 4</p><p><strong>Form:</strong> Device containing a liquid or silvery powder</p><p><strong>Effect:</strong> Sprays its contents up to a long distance, revealing all invisible creatures within short range of the targeted point for one round per cypher level. Affected invisible creatures remain visible if they move outside the area, and those outside the area become visible if they enter the area.</p>","archived":false,"basic":{"level":"1d6+4","identified":true},"settings":{"general":{"nameUnidentified":""}}},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"cyphersystem","systemVersion":"2.5.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1683654328318,"modifiedTime":1683655050998,"lastModifiedBy":"yThCrv1jSfPXOC2U"},"_id":"r5QRL7OjGkDkUw7y","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"yThCrv1jSfPXOC2U":3}}
